@host = https://localhost:7186

### 1. Generate JWT Token
POST {{host}}/api/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "expirationMinutes": 1200
}

###

### 2. Health Check (no auth required)
GET {{host}}/api/agify/health

###

